Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.75,0:00:12.21,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.29,0:00:17.96,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,照亮了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.03,0:00:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs38\pos(450,390)\1c&HFFFFFF&}海底两万里 / {\fs18}蓝宝石之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.93,0:00:30.03,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌懦弱的人 无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:36.54,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在做梦之前 我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.12,0:00:44.11,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心中的音乐盒开启 发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.19,0:00:51.36,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.43,0:01:00.10,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.17,0:01:05.58,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.64,0:01:10.60,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't forget to try in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.68,0:01:15.55,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.32,0:01:22.89,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.23,0:01:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强他们迫降在 非洲大陆的某个村落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.43,0:01:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚竟对在那里认识的少年 哈马哈马一见钟情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.97,0:01:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让强的心情变得非常复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.54,0:01:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,另一方面 大王因为喝下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.78,0:01:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,村里神殿的『红色果实的汁液』 而失控狂奔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.85,0:01:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因此被打着村里财宝歪主意的 一群恶徒捉住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,恶徒对哈马哈马要求 以宝物来交换大王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.19,0:01:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王的下场会如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:57.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚的恋情会有结果吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.63,0:02:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,时间只剩24小时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强他们的大王夺回作战 即将展开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:07.49,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,33 大王救援作战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.84,0:02:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在那之前你就先去替宝物 掸掸灰尘把它擦亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那道声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.42,0:02:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那道声音…那个长相…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大姐头 危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.22,0:02:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不会忘记的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.45,0:02:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,冈萨雷斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.49,0:02:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,冈萨雷斯？\N冈萨雷斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大姐头 你要做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.59,0:02:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这真是令人怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.23,0:02:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我记得你是意大利的 葛兰迪丝·格兰帕对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.97,0:02:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,相隔10年能在这片 辽阔的非洲大陆相遇 也算有缘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 冈萨雷斯大人 你们认识吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 冈萨雷斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.08,0:02:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个女的 好像一副跟您很熟的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.28,0:02:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是以前的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.95,0:02:52.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想对我旧情复燃罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:02:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.22,0:02:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.52,0:03:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为不小心想了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个人是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.73,0:03:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然会在这种地方 遇到那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一定是世上最不走运的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.67,0:03:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个混蛋在这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然带着女人 特地跑到非洲来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.61,0:03:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还自以为是凶神恶煞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱之深则恨之更深是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,0:03:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说我对冈萨雷斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我能明白女人恋爱时的心境
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.45,0:03:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,女人心应该就跟这些水一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有时冰冷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.39,0:03:37.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有时却热到会烫伤人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:40.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从高处流往低处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.33,0:03:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遵循自然的法则
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,流到正在等着我的心上人身边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.31,0:03:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 洗澡水要好好烧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,害我差点就烫伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.11,0:03:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.35,0:03:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别看啦 色狼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰坦也修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们去救大王吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.97,0:04:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.30,0:04:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在大王的性命 有如风中残烛的此时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们竟然还有心情洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:25.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大姐头竟然也跟着不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 敌人竟然会是 自己的初恋情人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.15,0:04:32.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大姐头好像相当沮丧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是因果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.82,0:04:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 接下来的问题才大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.72,0:04:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这下说不定会旧情复燃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,旧情复燃？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,恨之深则爱之更深
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只希望大姐头别又发病了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我去跟那家伙交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无论有什么样的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们都还是10年前的旧识
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,见面不到5分钟 就会沉醉在往事里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:05:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,靠我这身美到 像是变了个人的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.01,0:05:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,必能让他对我如痴如狂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是 对方是靠骗人为生的不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我就把他骗回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我才不会输给那些小女生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.86,0:05:12.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后趁机叫哈马哈马救回大王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.36,0:05:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们什么都不必做？\N我们什么都不必做？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.60,0:05:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她说哈马哈马会把大王救回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚说的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.57,0:05:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 你不能因为这样就泄气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.87,0:05:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚否定了 我们辛苦建立的科学文明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们绝不能就这样闷着不反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:37.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果这么轻易放弃 就称不上是男子汉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.95,0:05:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,既然娜蒂亚要找哈马哈马帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.22,0:05:43.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我们就抢先去把大王救回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让娜蒂亚见识到 近代科学的真正实力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.39,0:05:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这么一来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.46,0:05:52.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她一定会对你刮目相看的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要还是个男人 就不能输给那个卑鄙小人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:06:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 等着瞧吧 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.65,0:06:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:13.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,村里的宝物被开了个洞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那只是个罐头罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.49,0:06:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 那并不是一般的罐头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.82,0:06:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是很宝贵的罐头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.53,0:06:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王干的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哈马哈马 这一定是冈萨雷斯所为
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.17,0:06:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然把村里的宝物吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:31.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他实在太过份了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:33.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再这样下去 大王会有生命危险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们快去救它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:36.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大姐头不见了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.01,0:06:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们快去救大王吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她也不在帐棚里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,0:06:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.08,0:06:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是去跟冈萨雷斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,旧情复燃？\N旧情复燃？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.26,0:06:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,站着说话也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:01.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不如坐下来好好聊聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我跟你可没有话需要坐下来聊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快点把大王还来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.47,0:07:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:10.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是说那只小狮子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:11.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.71,0:07:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那群人一定会拿宝物来换的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.48,0:07:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,毕竟狮子是那个村子的守护神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们不会见死不救的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再说 我这个人可没坏到那种地步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不愧是冈萨雷斯大人 好高明的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真不愧是您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.99,0:07:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这下子宝物 就是我们的囊中物了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哈马哈马
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只靠我们两个人 要怎么把大王救出来？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.57,0:07:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 用不着担心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们是从未打过任何败仗的 无敌民族
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.11,0:07:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那些家伙根本不足为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能让你如此不择手段
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个村子的宝物 到底是什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你连这都不晓得 就跑来这个村子吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.92,0:07:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的是什么稀世珍宝吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.39,0:08:00.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请您…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,慢慢享用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来为你的眼睛干杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 这样就能争取到一些时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下来只要等娜蒂亚他们 把大王救走就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.71,0:08:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就快离开森林了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这种时候如果有气球的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就能拟出更好的作战计划了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们要怎样把大王救出来？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这种时候用不着耍小手段
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.22,0:08:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直接冲进去！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰迪丝还没来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.03,0:08:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下来我一个人过去就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 你就待在这里等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:49.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哈马哈马 我来当诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,诱饵？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.44,0:08:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我会引开冈萨雷斯的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:55.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就趁机去救大王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:08:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.32,0:09:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是说 你说的那根银柱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:06.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就在那个村子里是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要得到那根银柱 我就能成为欧洲第一…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:13.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 是世界第一的大富翁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,银柱…世界第一的大富翁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.00,0:09:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么样？葛兰迪丝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,10年前我们都还太年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当时我唯一想要的就是金钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.81,0:09:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 在那之后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.64,0:09:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想要的东西 都能以金钱获得满足
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.15,0:09:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不虞匮乏的富裕生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.85,0:09:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,却也仅止于此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.39,0:09:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在这10年中 我总觉得有什么缺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.36,0:09:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你晓得那是什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,冈…冈萨雷斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就别再追究那段 不愉快的过往
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以后就和我一同 开创蔷薇色的人生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰迪丝 你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.71,0:10:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我这样是为了当诱饵…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好过份 真下流
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.21,0:10:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你果然还是背叛我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:08.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不配知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.06,0:10:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么都看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王 大王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我来救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嘘 安静点 出声音会被发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.75,0:10:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是葛兰坦的气球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.46,0:10:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里是玛莉缝的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:47.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.89,0:10:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.53,0:10:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,重要的是现在该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在看不到前面的情况下 直接冲进去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是自寻死路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.93,0:10:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,中止 中止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不得已了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:10:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,中止救援行动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个狠毒的男人 就是你的初恋情人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原本只是诈欺兼小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.18,0:11:13.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在则是连绑架监禁都干
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也算是堕落得真彻底
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.79,0:11:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不敢当
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.99,0:11:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只是为了要让世人了解非洲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才会收集沉睡在非洲大陆上的 众多文化资产罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,非洲有许多珍贵的文化资产
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再说 我是透过和平的方式 与村人协调请他们让出宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.81,0:11:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这也是现代人应有的礼仪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,冈萨雷斯大人总是绅士作风
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太迷人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.71,0:11:45.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,冈萨雷斯虽然是个天才诈欺师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但他的手下只有两名金发女子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就力量而言 绝对是对我方有利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是我们的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王 娜蒂亚 葛兰迪丝 目前被关在他的装甲车中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是万一…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.23,0:12:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们听好了 要是万一 村里的宝物只不过是个罐头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且里头的东西已经被大王 吞进胃袋的这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.77,0:12:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被冈萨雷斯晓得的话 会如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.78,0:12:19.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,目前一切都只是纯属想像
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 到时不只是大王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:24.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,连娜蒂亚与葛兰迪丝都会…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.32,0:12:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尤其是葛兰迪丝现在落入 10年前背叛她的初恋情人手中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想到她可能再次被骗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再次遭到那名 下流中年男子的毒手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:38.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就实在是坐立难安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.37,0:12:40.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不能放过他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.64,0:12:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该死的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾尔顿 冷静点…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我懂 你的心情我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:47.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你懂？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你会懂才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.25,0:12:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要去救葛兰迪丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:13:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别担心 村里的人很快就会 带宝物来救你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.99,0:13:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要忍耐到那个时候就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有人会带宝物来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:06.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.40,0:13:08.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为宝物已经没了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,话可不能随便乱说喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.74,0:13:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再说 那个宝物 只不过是个罐头罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根本就不值钱…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亏你长得那么可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.18,0:13:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要撒谎至少也该撒个 会让人相信的谎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.25,0:13:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,目前我方的战力有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,万能战车葛兰坦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,偶然在森林中发现的 葛兰坦专用气球
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,关于气球的状况 目前正在缝补破损处
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:36.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,预计不久便能完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很好 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.76,0:13:42.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这下我们就能从陆空两方 对那些家伙发动攻击了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.10,0:13:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么老是要我来补破洞啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.90,0:13:47.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,情况如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.64,0:13:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就快缝好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,冈萨雷斯的装甲车 位在丘陵地带中心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,属于视野相当良好的地形
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.51,0:13:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要执行利用葛兰坦 或是气球的奇袭战术
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是相当不利的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你这是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.22,0:14:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算我们有这么多装备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还是什么都办不到是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.26,0:14:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们是绝对输不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.83,0:14:13.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,除非拥有必胜的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,否则无法执行计划
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.20,0:14:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶的哈马哈马
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他到底在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,冈萨雷斯大人一生起气来 不晓得会做出什么事喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那只小狮子活不久了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.98,0:14:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我才不会让你这个骗子杀它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:36.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且哈马哈马他 至今从未打过任何败仗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你还真敢说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.82,0:14:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,女性要典雅含蓄才会有人爱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.76,0:14:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对吧\N您说的对 冈萨雷斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.13,0:14:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,女人果然还是得典雅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.93,0:14:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,女人果然还是得含蓄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.23,0:14:50.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.50,0:14:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们还是有胜算
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要我们沿着 流经装甲车南侧河道接近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.07,0:14:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就不会被对方发现
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:15:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能够轻易地攻进敌营
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,河道是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 这河道太窄 葛兰坦无法通过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用不着担心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.58,0:15:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们已经在 哈马哈马他们的独木舟上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.02,0:15:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加装葛兰坦的水中推进器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,目前随时都能出发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.46,0:15:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现代科学与传统文化携手合作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正可说是哈马哈马他们 与葛兰迪丝军团的共同作战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我该做什么好？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.04,0:15:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们要靠葛兰坦来吸引住 冈萨雷斯的目光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:34.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就从正面冲向 冈萨雷斯的装甲车
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为我们制造机会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.68,0:15:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,诱饵是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.32,0:15:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过啊 韩森
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么一来 葛兰坦会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.49,0:15:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但现在最要紧的是将我方的 两名女性与一只狮子平安救出
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这种情况 也只好牺牲葛兰坦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.66,0:15:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,既然你都这么说了 那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由我来当诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.40,0:15:57.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我会彻底吸引住他们的目光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:15:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们就趁这个机会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.57,0:16:04.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让大王喝下哈马哈马村子里 流传的红色果实浓缩汁液
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.68,0:16:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 只要喝了这个 不论是谁都能元气百倍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:11.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么一来 大王就能以 百倍的力量挣脱十字架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.62,0:16:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后再将这个机械大王塞进去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来个偷天换日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.59,0:16:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很好 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.69,0:16:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,问题在于要如何让大王喝下这个 又不被冈萨雷斯他们发现？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.93,0:16:25.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要把这个 送进大王的嘴巴里就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.60,0:16:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.76,0:16:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我可是个射击天才喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么要由我来当诱饵？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.77,0:16:36.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为我们很看好 艾尔顿伯爵大人的驾驶技术啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.94,0:16:38.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你好奸诈 桑森
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是给艾尔顿驾驶 一定又会被他弄坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.71,0:16:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你刚才不是说了 就算坏掉也无所谓吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果是它自己坏掉就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:48.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不要它被人弄坏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快点出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那好吧 我也要坐上葛兰坦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.96,0:16:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我跟玛莉就搭气球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:16:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你负责的是掉包机械大王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.06,0:16:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以要搭哈马哈马的独木舟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:01.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就那么决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们的目的只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.44,0:17:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是从冈萨雷斯的装甲车中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.37,0:17:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,救出大王 娜蒂亚以及大姐头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.81,0:17:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为此手段稍微粗暴 也是没办法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.64,0:17:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,祝大家顺利成功
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.41,0:17:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们村子在打仗前 都会吆喝打气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.58,0:17:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么吆喝？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.58,0:17:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安它巴来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.69,0:17:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安它巴来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 这可真是颗稀奇的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.18,0:17:52.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你别乱碰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.52,0:17:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这并不是你所想像的那种石头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.75,0:17:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你竟然碰了我一直想碰 却碰不到的蔚蓝之水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的眼光看来的确没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会闪烁发光的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:08.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在非洲旅行了这么久 还是第一次看到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.63,0:18:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才不给你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.24,0:18:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不能开快一点吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.14,0:18:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,像我这样的贵族
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可学不来桑森那种 粗鲁的驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我就让你学会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.16,0:18:33.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,独木舟还没到喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.36,0:18:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶 强他们在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.89,0:18:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我会用这台机械大王 将娜蒂亚救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 我答应过娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.67,0:18:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我会将她救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:45.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用了啦 哈马哈马
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚就由我来救
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.74,0:18:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你去救葛兰迪丝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.47,0:18:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 我不能撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.47,0:18:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要遵守承诺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.78,0:18:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,冈萨雷斯大人 把那颗漂亮的石头送我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:19:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要 给我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.25,0:19:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们两个同时撒娇想要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这下我可要伤脑筋啰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.43,0:19:10.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行 那并不是普通的宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.80,0:19:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要把蔚蓝之水 送给那种女人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.03,0:19:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们总是全心全意伺候我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再说 这些女孩们 还保有着你已失去的年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.81,0:19:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.17,0:19:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然看起来成熟了点 但我也才20几而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.78,0:19:27.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 这位阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.34,0:19:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就算四舍五入也才20喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也是才20岁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:35.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,光是肌肤的弹性就不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:41.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,既然已经忍无可忍 那就用不着再忍了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王昏过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.25,0:20:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们竟然嘲笑我是 『阿姨』还有什么『化妆太厚了』
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.66,0:20:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好难受…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.56,0:20:20.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拿回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.83,0:20:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喔 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,乖乖把那颗宝石交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.00,0:20:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 用不着理他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.80,0:20:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他才没胆对我开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就难说了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要靠我的发明 把娜蒂亚救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要靠回旋镖 把娜蒂亚救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.89,0:20:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是哈马哈马
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.83,0:20:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,趁这个机会溜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.30,0:20:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:57.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.64,0:20:58.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.64,0:21:05.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.11,0:21:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.98,0:21:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是葛兰坦…\N是葛兰坦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:16.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要怎么停下来？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.82,0:21:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,踩刹车啦 刹车
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚\N娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.07,0:21:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚\N娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.21,0:21:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哈马哈马…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.41,0:21:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚！\N娜蒂亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.16,0:21:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,JUMBO
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.76,0:21:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这可说是科学的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.06,0:21:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.30,0:22:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不认为他会因此得到教训
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.20,0:22:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶的葛兰迪丝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是冈萨雷斯大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.41,0:22:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那只小狮子还在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.14,0:22:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要这只狮子在我们手上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.38,0:22:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就能再和对方谈判
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.31,0:22:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 这只小狮子的颜色有点怪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.78,0:22:21.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,声音也有点怪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.56,0:22:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在机械大王身上 动了一点小手脚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.93,0:22:35.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太过份了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.83,0:22:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎么可以做出那么暴力的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.97,0:22:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.44,0:22:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我没办法遵守承诺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.57,0:22:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要紧的 哈马哈马
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.01,0:22:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要你来我就很开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我来介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.08,0:22:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这位是我们邻村的英勇战士 穆菈穆菈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.51,0:22:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,JUMBO
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.32,0:22:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,穆菈穆菈是我日后的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.68,0:22:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,日后的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.52,0:22:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妻子？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.09,0:22:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 我们从小就约定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.39,0:22:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是未婚妻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.56,0:23:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,穆菈穆菈知道塔提苏司的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.00,0:23:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然绕了点路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.11,0:23:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 能找到娜蒂亚的出生地 不也可喜可贺吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.08,0:23:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.38,0:23:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当伤心事成为过去 也会成为闪闪发光的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.48,0:23:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.68,0:23:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幸好娜蒂亚身边 还有一个总是不离不弃的男人在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.65,0:23:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.85,0:23:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大姐头的身边也有许多男人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.56,0:23:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对…\N对…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.56,0:23:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们两个请打起精神来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.93,0:23:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.13,0:23:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你还有我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.66,0:23:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 我跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.87,0:23:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.80,0:23:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我最讨厌你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.64,0:23:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真不讨人喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.27,0:23:54.47,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.55,0:24:02.51,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么应付心中的焦急才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.59,0:24:07.68,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就要看不清远方的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.76,0:24:12.09,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喃喃自语 仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.16,0:24:20.93,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与你的约定耀眼闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.00,0:24:31.04,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Try 安慰的话语 是传达不到内心的风
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.11,0:24:39.85,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然背负的不安逐渐膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.92,0:24:44.09,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但这是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.16,0:24:48.72,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一个人应该也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.80,0:24:58.14,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使跌倒或感到迷惘 仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.02,0:25:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最担心因为失恋 而受到打击之娜蒂亚的人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.39,0:25:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然还是强
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.16,0:25:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 实在让人看不太下去
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.73,0:25:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对强来说 发明比我重要多了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.20,0:25:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强的新发明是否能获得 娜蒂亚的芳心呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.14,0:25:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海底两万里 下一回 『心爱的娜蒂亚』
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.84,0:25:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要看喔\N要看喔
